   <title class="- topic/title ">Reconciliation</title>
   <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">X-Author provides a reconciliation feature which enables changes made to smart fields in an agreement document, outside of the Salesforce/X-Author environment, to be reconciled with the data held in the Agreement record in Salesforce.</shortdesc>
