   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">In a typical scenario where an agreement document is sent to an external party for negotiation, the external party will make changes to the document as part of the negotiation. If the changes to the document involve data belonging to the Agreement record, reconciliation provides the mechanism to ensure the values in the document and the Agreement record are reconciled.</p>
